Title: HK Groups Incident Response Procedure
Version: 1.0
Authority Level: High

1. Objective
Ensure rapid detection, containment, and resolution of security and system incidents.

2. Incident Categories
Data breach

Unauthorized access

Service outage

Trading system anomaly

3. Response Steps
3.1 Detection
Identify incident via monitoring alerts or reports

3.2 Containment
Isolate affected systems

Disable compromised credentials

3.3 Investigation
Review logs

Identify root cause

3.4 Resolution
Patch vulnerabilities

Restore affected services

3.5 Reporting
Incidents must be reported within 24 hours

Compliance team notified for dataâ€‘related incidents

4. Logging Requirements
All actions taken during incident response must be logged.


